Name: Santino Roma
Location: United States
Time Zone: America/New_York
Position Applying For: Ingame Moderator if open
Bio: 16 years old, ive been coding for maybe 1 year ive been playing runescape private servers for around 3-4 years i have been co-owner of a server called nexon-world and i have only been a player moderator on 1 server i like to have fun with my friends and i also like to spend a lot of my time on my laptop with runescape private servers
Why you deserve this position:im a people person im only 16 i like talking to people on different servers and getting to know them i also help a lot of people out of rune-server forums with server problems and client problems and i like to help people ingame with stuff im a very nice person and im positive you wolnt regret chosing me
